query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stats')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('anova',
'arima',
'clustering',
'cross-validation',
'data-visualization',
'deep-learning',
'estimation',
'generalized-linear-model',
'maximum-likelihood',
'multiple-regression',
'references',
'statistical-significance',
'variance');
